x_n
A_1\ldots A_{n-1}A_n=I
A_n=(-1)^{n+1}(A-x_nI)
A_1+(-1)^nA_n=x_nI
 p(x)+(-1)^{n+1}=(-1)^n\left(\det(A_1-xI)-1\right)=(x-x_1)\ldots(x-x_n). 
 (-1)^{n+1}I = (A_1-x_1)\ldots(A_1-x_{n-1}I)(A_1-x_nI) = A_1\ldots A_{n-1}(A_1-x_nI). 
